---
title: Korma Style Spiced Chicken and Pepper Skewers with Mango Chutney, Wedges and Baby Leaf Salad
description: This Korma Style Spiced Chicken and Pepper Skewers is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
